{
  "stem": "10859.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ironically, that time already, Hitler start organizing the ghettos in 1941.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From 1941 till 1942, that year was organized ghettos practically everywhere where were Jewish people lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The idea from a ghetto-- I don't know if you know-- is the reason that, when the time comes, he had his plans to kill all those people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he wouldn't have no problem to go around and look if he's Jewish or if he's not Jewish, he's Polish or Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This way, you know, he had them separated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whenever he wants to kill them, he'll get them all out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the way he planned it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was-- came home, it still didn't change too much, our life-- [LAUGHS] --in that small little village, like for the Russians, like for the Polish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in our own house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no ghetto, because we-- they didn't have to make a ghetto in our place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived whatever we had from the farm, like before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But suddenly, it's like the heaven fall down to the earth-- is when they came in one day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we never see Germans-- only in Trochenbrod, in the next little town, was, I think, two or three officers staying there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, is the Ukrainian police did all the job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to come with a bunch of the Ukrainian police, and that's all they did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took out all the cows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cows-- all we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took them all, cleaned them out, and took them away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they had meat for free, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was very bad for us, because that was our life, you know, to help us out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have milk.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
